ajority\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"skateboarding athletes\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"teenagers\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is no science behind why youngsters achieve such success in the sport,' says Team GB on its official page.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1116, \"end\": 1123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9987488444670224, \"rank\": 0.0012527227364884175, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no science\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"youngsters\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"such success\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"its official page\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Although it's important to note that the likes of Team GB's Andy Macdonald will turn 51 during Paris 2024.'\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9987488444670224, \"rank\": 0.0012527227364884175, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1208, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"score\": 0.9999978194979248, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Macdonald\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the likes\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB says: 'The sport attracts young children and teens through its comradery in the skatepark and the enticement of getting a trick just right.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9987488444670224, \"rank\": 0.0012527227364884175, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sport\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"young children\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"teens\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"its comradery\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"the skatepark\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"the enticement\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"a trick\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Add that to the fearless nature of Olympic skateboarders, teenagers seem to be dominating the sporting stage.'\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fearless nature\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic skateboarders\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"teenagers\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting stage\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's that comradery and fearlessness that BBC commentator Ed Leigh believes contributes to why skateboarders are so young - as well as the fact their bodies are able to tolerate the brutal impact the sport has on them.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1581, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ed_Leigh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ed Leigh\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ed_Leigh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ed_Leigh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that comradery\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1542}, {\"ngram\": \"fearlessness\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"skateboarders\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"so young - as well as the fact\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"their bodies\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"the brutal impact\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's terrifyingly physical and you have to understand how much commitment it takes,' he told the i newspaper at Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999998668195165, \"rank\": 1.325681809563395e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how much commitment\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"the i newspaper\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Anyone who has stepped on a skateboard has fallen off, and there is a good saying, it does not matter how rich you are, you can not buy a trick, you have to pay with pain.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anyone\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"a skateboard\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"a good saying\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"a trick\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That's the only way around it.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only way\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's something shared between all skateboarders.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"all skateboarders\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A camaraderie.\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A camaraderie\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You know to get that good you have overcome some big slams and stayed committed to it.\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some big slams\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Action sports are based in skill acquisition.\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Action sports\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2243}, {\"ngram\": \"skill acquisition\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The younger you are, the bendier and softer you are when you try and get those skills, the quicker you can recover.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those skills\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You have athletes by 21, 22, talking about recovery time, the fact is they can not just keep skating.'\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2411}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery time\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2450}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB star Macdonald believes age is nothing but a number, however - and is proving it by the mere fact he's in contention in the men's park event on August 7.\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Macdonald\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"the mere fact\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2603}, {\"ngram\": \"contention\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngra